{"tid":1769843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城門水塘發現137公升腐蝕性化學品 警：不排除與中大實驗室危險品失竊有關","createTime":"2019-12-05T07:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:01:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":204,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9281abe3fa770aad0570c95d4572dcd509d520","tid":1769843,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"警方聯同消防員在城門水塘附近的山坡發現危險化學品，不排除可以用作製做燃燒彈。<br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科總督察譚子偉表示，在現場發現59支共重約137公升腐蝕性化學品，不排除與早前中大實驗室失竊的危險品有關，警方正全力進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，化學品收藏於有草叢遮蔽的山坡位置，與水塘有一定距離，暫未發現有洩漏情況，已通知水務署，會再作出跟進。"},{"pid":"770b80030e602db4870bc58330579e0fddac48df","tid":1769843,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496108-20191205.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496108-20191205.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=524a15a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496108-20191205.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aac7ad2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496108-20191205.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fe9fba03a296407b0e6e421530b1581e16a1d5b1","tid":1769843,"uid":51701,"like":221,"dislike":1,"score":220,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"總次屈左示威者先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab03e8c5a397049bd2e546dcc2c03e859041595","tid":1769843,"uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"咁冇手尾"},{"pid":"7b8ece37e3a6aa31426c8ab31e355ec40be9c79d","tid":1769843,"uid":5591,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"Con受 週圍hea"},{"pid":"63e96a0c3f358d25be1e045a3977780a8acbbb71","tid":1769843,"uid":21262